{"tid":1856992,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"屯門大媽戴政府CSI口罩","createTime":"2020-02-02T03:08:11.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-02T04:46:35.000Z","uid":327658,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"5b7acf137fc4045015fa71712073797a230344be","tid":1856992,"uid":327658,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-02T03:08:11.000Z","msg":"呢個政府完全信唔過！<br />\n<br />\n新型冠狀病毒引起的武漢肺炎肆虐本港，市民四出搶購口罩，甚至不惜通宵冒著寒風排隊。而政府內部的口罩供應，是由懲教工業組（Correctional Services Industries）中的成年女性在囚人士生產，口罩會印有 CSI 字眼以作辨識，只供衛生署、食環署及消防等部門使用，市面上未有公開發售。<br />\n<br />\n但今日（1日）網上流傳一組圖片，指於屯門公園的跳舞大媽配戴着CSI口罩，政府發言人澄清，在疫情發生前有向一些非政府機構供應口罩，因此坊間有人使用懲教署生產的口罩不足為奇。<br />\n<br />\n新聞來源：<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/%E6%94%BF%E6%83%85/428824/%E6%AD%A6%E6%BC%A2%E8%82%BA%E7%82%8E-%E5%B1%AF%E9%96%80%E5%A4%A7%E5%AA%BD%E6%88%B4csi%E5%8F%A3%E7%BD%A9-%E6%94%BF%E5%BA%9C%E6%BE%84%E6%B8%85-%E6%9B%BE%E5%90%91%E9%9D%9E%E6%94%BF%E5%BA%9C%E6%A9%9F%E6%A7%8B%E4%BE%9B%E6%87%89\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%25E6%2594%25BF%25E6%2583%2585%2F428824%2F%25E6%25AD%25A6%25E6%25BC%25A2%25E8%2582%25BA%25E7%2582%258E-%25E5%25B1%25AF%25E9%2596%2580%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E5%25AA%25BD%25E6%2588%25B4csi%25E5%258F%25A3%25E7%25BD%25A9-%25E6%2594%25BF%25E5%25BA%259C%25E6%25BE%2584%25E6%25B8%2585-%25E6%259B%25BE%25E5%2590%2591%25E9%259D%259E%25E6%2594%25BF%25E5%25BA%259C%25E6%25A9%259F%25E6%25A7%258B%25E4%25BE%259B%25E6%2587%2589&d=ANzGKs6Ysw%2B%2BKy1wioRXt6crr%2FRj6%2FCkFD6x6yFTuc4%3D&h=881f2a5b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/%E6%94%BF%E6%83%85/428824/%E6%AD%A6%E6%BC%A2%E8%82%BA%E7%82%8E-%E5%B1%AF%E9%96%80%E5%A4%A7%E5%AA%BD%E6%88%B4csi%E5%8F%A3%E7%BD%A9-%E6%94%BF%E5%BA%9C%E6%BE%84%E6%B8%85-%E6%9B%BE%E5%90%91%E9%9D%9E%E6%94%BF%E5%BA%9C%E6%A9%9F%E6%A7%8B%E4%BE%9B%E6%87%89</a>"},{"pid":"3f97db506394c46b45e2ce291ca721caf2e7cd4b","tid":1856992,"uid":28818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-02T04:45:11.000Z","msg":"好多個post講緊啦<br />\n<br />